  ./tools/fw hil-wifi-monitor
  ./tools/fw hil-wifi-run

Notes:
  - All developer-facing validation runs inside Docker by default.
  - Containers write back to the bind mount using the caller UID:GID.
  - Set DOCKER_BIN, FW_HOST_IMAGE, FW_DOCS_IMAGE, FW_SDK_IMAGE, FW_RUN_USER,
